OL,3,CGovernment to review how Manchester
OL,4,Cbomb plotter could attack prison guards
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,7,FYoussef reports
OL,9,FA review will be carried out following
OL,10,FManchester Arena bomb plotter Hashem
OL,11,FAbedi attacked three prison officers
OL,12,Fwith hot oil and home-made weapons,
OL,13,Fthe Ministry of Justice has said.
OL,15,FAbedi threw hot cooking oil over three
OL,16,Fofficers on Saturday 12 April before
OL,17,Fstabbing them with "home-made
OL,18,Fweapons", the Prison Officers'
OL,19,FAssociation (POA) said.
