OL,3,CGovernment to review how Manchester
OL,4,Cbomb plotter could attack prison guards
OL,6,FThe officers sustained life-
OL,7,Fthreatening injuries including burns,
OL,8,Fscalds and stab wounds in the
OL,9,F"unprovoked" and "vicious" attack in
OL,10,FHMP Frankland, County Durham,
OL,11,Faccording to the trade union covering
OL,12,Fprison staff.
OL,14,FTwo officers sustained "severe stab
OL,15,Fwounds" but are in a stable condition
OL,16,Fin hospital, POA's national chairman
OL,17,Fsaid on Sunday morning. A female
OL,18,Fofficer had been discharged by 4pm on
OL,19,FSaturday.
