OL,4,Cbomb plotter could attack prison guards
OL,6,FAnnouncing the review into the
OL,7,Fincident, a Ministry of Justice
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Our thoughts
OL,9,Fremain with the two prison officers
OL,10,Fstill in hospital as they recover.
OL,12,F"There will be a full review into how
OL,13,Fthis attack was able to happen,
OL,14,Falongside the separate police inquiry.
OL,16,F"The Government will do whatever it
OL,17,Ftakes to keep our hardworking staff
OL,18,Fsafe."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
