OL,6,FCounter Terrorism Policing (CTP) NE is
OL,7,Fleading the investigation into the
OL,8,F"serious assault".
OL,10,FAbedi was convicted of assisting with
OL,11,Fthe Manchester terror plot, in which
OL,12,Fhis suicide bomber brother Salman
OL,13,FAbedi killed 22 people by detonating a
OL,14,Fhomemade rucksack-bomb in a crowd of
OL,15,Fconcert-goers.
