OL,6,FAbedi was handed a record-breaking 55-
OL,7,Fyear minimum term in August 2020 which
OL,8,Fhe is currently serving at the
OL,9,FCategory A HMP Frankland.
OL,11,FCategory A is the highest level of
OL,12,Fsecurity and Frankland has housed
OL,13,Fother notorious inmates, including
OL,14,FFusilier Lee Rigby's terrorist killer
OL,15,FMichael Adebolajo, Yorkshire Ripper
OL,16,FPeter Sutcliffe, and Charles Bronson.
OL,17,FFrankland also has a separation centre.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
